OL,6,FPeople suffering with an eating
OL,7,Fdisorder that makes them avoid certain
OL,8,Ffoods should be offered specialist
OL,9,Ftreatment amid a "dramatic increase"
OL,10,Fin those seeking help, a charity has
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FThe number of people seeking help for
OL,14,Fa previously little-known eating
OL,15,Fdisorder called Avoidant/Restrictive
OL,16,FFood Intake Disorder () has risen
OL,17,Fsevenfold since 2018, charity Beat
OL,18,Fsaid.
