OL,3,CRise in people seeking help for
OL,4,Cpreviously little-known eating disorder
OL,6,FThe figure is up from 295 calls in
OL,7,F2018. Andrew Radford, chief executive
OL,8,Fof Beat, described the spike as
OL,9,F"extremely worrying".
OL,11,FHe said: "All too often we hear from
OL,12,Fpeople who have been unable to get
OL,13,Ftreatment close to home, or have faced
OL,14,Fwaits of months or even years to get
OL,15,Fthe help they need."
OL,17,FWhat is ARFID?
OL,19,FARFID is when someone avoids certain
OL,20,Ffoods, limits how much they eat or
OL,21,Fdoes both.
