OL,6,FBeliefs about weight or body shape are
OL,7,Fnot reasons why people develop ARFID.
OL,9,FPossible reasons for ARFID include:
OL,11,FBeliefs about weight and shape do not
OL,12,Fcontribute to the avoidance or
OL,13,Frestriction of food intake.
OL,15,FMr Radford added: "ARFID is an eating
OL,16,Fdisorder that rarely gets the
OL,17,Fattention it deserves, and it's
OL,18,Funacceptable that that seems to apply
OL,19,Fto funding, too.
