OL,6,F"Now is the time for to ensure that
OL,7,Fanyone who needs support can get it
OL,8,Ffrom trained and fully equipped teams
OL,9,Facross the country."
OL,11,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "During the
OL,12,Fpandemic, referrals for eating
OL,13,Fdisorders for children increased by
OL,14,Falmost 50% and the NHS is clear that
OL,15,Fimproving care for people with an
OL,16,Feating disorder including ARFID is
OL,17,Fvital, with investment, targeted
OL,18,Fsupport and training helping to
OL,19,Fdevelop community eating disorder
OL,20,Fteams in all areas in England.
